column15: Inflation-adjusted prices are adjusted by the CPI-U-RS.
Prior to Q4 1977 they are adjusted by the CPI - All items less shelter.
The CPI-U-RS (Research Series) is available at http://www.clevelandfed.org/Research/data/US-Inflation/chartsdata/
The CPI all items less shelter is available at http://data.bls.gov/cgi-bin/srgate by entering series id CUUR0000SA0L2.
Owner-equivalent rent index is available at http://data.bls.gov/cgi-bin/srgate by entering series id CUUR0000SEHC.
